For lifecycle of activity, there're seven activities, including
OnCreate(), onStart(),  onResume(), onPause(), OnStop(), onRestart(), onDestroy()

When a activity is invoked, onCreate(), onStart(), onResume() methods are invoked.
When you press the triangle button, back, onPause(), onStop(), onDestroy() methods are invoked.
When you press the home button, onPause(), onStop() methods are invoked.

